        html:'<table><tbody><tr><td><img alt="" height="40" src="http://efundi.nwu.ac.za/access/content/group/10cda5f9-d75a-4928-a31a-2f3b9a29a9de/small/ICON_discuss.png" width="40" /></td><td>&nbsp;</td><td><h3>Discussion/ Bespreking&nbsp;</h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>Forum: Class discussion / Group&nbsp;discussion</strong></h3><p>Welcome to the&nbsp;discussion forum. <span style="color:#2980b9">This is a space where you can interact with your fellow students and lecturer about general questions and ideas /&nbsp;You are expected to collaborate with your group members about specific topics posted to the forum.</span>&nbsp;To get started, select your group/topic from the topic list below.&nbsp;To post, click on &ldquo;Start a New Conversation&rdquo;.</p><p><strong>Need help?</strong>&nbsp;For more information on how to use the Forum visit the Help page found on the eFundi homepage, select User Guide.</p><p><strong>Instructions:</strong><br />Please join the discussion on the Forum topic: (Name of topic). Access the link to the topic below and answer the following questions:</p><ol><li>Question 1</li><li>Question 2</li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol start="1"><li>Add a post of / Post at least (200 / number of) words in which&nbsp;you refer to at least (2) sources to support your statements.</li><li>Provide an insightful comment on at least (1) other post.</li></ol><p><strong>Deadline: [DATE]</strong></p><p><img alt="enlightened" height="23" src="/library/editor/ckeditor/plugins/smiley/images/lightbulb.png" title="enlightened" width="23" /><span style="color:#c0392b"><span aria-label="enlightened image widget" contenteditable="false" role="region" tabindex="-1"></span>Pick between the two blue sentences and heading for a&nbsp;<strong>Class-wide discussion</strong> OR <strong>Group&nbsp;</strong><strong>discussion</strong>.<br /><strong><em>*Delete this note, for lecturers only.</em></strong></span></p>'
